          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-ink-muted">When you chip in, you help keep Ferni free for others. You're not buying a product — you're helping us build something we believe everyone deserves. As a thank you, we'll unlock some perks.</div>
        </details>
        
        <details class="reveal group faq-item bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg border border-ink/5 overflow-hidden transition-all">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 p-6 cursor-pointer font-display font-semibold text-lg text-ink">
