          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-ink-muted">Absolutely. Increase, decrease, or stop your support anytime. No hard feelings. We're grateful for any time you've been with us.</div>
        </details>
        
        <details class="reveal group faq-item bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg border border-ink/5 overflow-hidden transition-all">
